## Configuration

Key configuration options in `.env`:

```bash
# Environment
MMM_ENV=development

# Server
HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=8000

# Model training
TRAINING_WINDOW_DAYS=126
TEST_WINDOW_DAYS=14
N_BOOTSTRAP=1000

# File upload
MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB=100

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
USE_JSON_LOGGING=true
```

